item.title: 100 errors, what i mess up?
item.dc:creator: @Javacisnotrecognized _^_
item.description:
@Javacisnotrecognized wrote:

You can’t have a line return in the middle of a string of text. If you are going do to something like

sendMessage("You need an upgrading level of 
 ten to do that");

You will get the error.
It has to be

sendMessage("You have to have an upgrading level of ten to do that.");

Read full topic
